{"word":"G1487 - εἰ - ei - i - Forasmuch as","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἰ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ei"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>i"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Forasmuch as"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"ஆல் - முன்னிடை நிகழ்கால ஒருமை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"conditional particle, if an interrogative particle, whether,"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Conjunction / இணைப்புச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primary particle of conditionality; <i>if</i>, <i>whether</i>, <i>that</i>, etc.: - forasmuch as, if, that, ([al-]) though, whether. Often used in connection or composition with other particles, especially as in <a href=\"#/G1489 - εἴγε - eíge - i'-gheh/1489\">G1489</a>, <a href=\"#/G1490 - εἰ δὲ μή(γε) - ei dè mḗ(ge) - i deh may'-(gheh)/1490\">G1490</a>, <a href=\"#/G1499 - εἰ καί - ei kaí - i kahee/1499\">G1499</a>, <a href=\"#/G1508 - εἰ μή - ei mḗ - i may/1508\">G1508</a>, <a href=\"#/G1509 - εἰ μή τι - ei mḗ ti - i may tee/1509\">G1509</a>, <a href=\"#/G1512 - εἴ περ - eí per - i per/1512\">G1512</a>, <a href=\"#/G1513 - εἴ πως - eí pōs - i poce/1513\">G1513</a>, <a href=\"#/G1536 - εἴ τις - eí tis - i tis/1536\">G1536</a>, and <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a>. See also <a href=\"#/G1437 - ἐάν - eán - eh-an'/1437\">G1437</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}